{"id":608136,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/【cdtv】习近平再度口误-论坛闭幕式上读错提防/","date":"2019-03-27T16:21:17Z","modified":"2019-03-27T16:23:42Z","title":"【CDTV】习近平再度口误 论坛闭幕式上读错“提防”、“发酵”","content":"<p>3月27日，推特网友 ‏@gugufan1 截取了一段习近平在&#8221;中法全球治理论坛闭幕式&#8221;上的致辞，在1分40秒的视频中，习近平再次出现口误，将“提（di）防”、“发酵（jiao）”读为（ti）、（xiao）。在官方媒体的有关<a href=\"http://www.xinhuanet.com/world/2019-03/26/c_1124286578.htm\">报道</a>中，并没有出现习近平此段视频讲话。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">提(ti)防你，别发酵(xiao) <a href=\"https://t.co/WhMK1cx6PU\">pic.twitter.com/WhMK1cx6PU</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 凡谷谷 (@gugufan1) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/gugufan1/status/1110677407206440962?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 26, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/hiXZD65Bj74?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-608137\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2019_03_27_b31375cd209842f4b5015bea6b2c9cd1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2019_03_27_b31375cd209842f4b5015bea6b2c9cd1.jpeg 799w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2019_03_27_b31375cd209842f4b5015bea6b2c9cd1-300x201.jpeg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2019_03_27_b31375cd209842f4b5015bea6b2c9cd1-768x514.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/2019_03_27_b31375cd209842f4b5015bea6b2c9cd1-360x240.jpeg 360w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"shWqdQo7Sv\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/12/%e3%8